text: Jackson Rancheria is the landbase for the Jackson Rancheria of Me-Wuk Indians of California, a federally recognized tribe of Miwok people, located near Jackson, California. It is located in Amador County, about midway between Jackson and Pine Grove. The reservation operates the Jackson Rancheria Casino Resort, located on its territory. == Notes == Category:Miwok Category:Amador County, California Category:Native American tribes in California Category:Federally recognized tribes in the United States Category:American Indian reservations in California
